克里斯·海姆斯沃斯 (Chris Hemsworth) 意外以鼓手身份亮相罗马尼亚艾德·希兰 (Ed Sheeran) 演出https://www.nme.com/news/music/chris-hemsworth-makes-surprise-appearance-as-drummer-at-ed-sheeran-show-in-romania-3786878?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=chris-海姆斯沃斯在罗马尼亚艾德希兰演出中以鼓手身份惊艳亮相Daniel PetersSun, 25 Aug 2024 10:08:42 +0000 Film NewsMusic NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3786878 <p><img width="1392" height="884" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/EdSheeran-ChrisHemsworth-Getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="艾德·希兰克里斯·海姆斯沃斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/EdSheeran-ChrisHemsworth-Getty.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/EdSheeran-ChrisHemsworth-Getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/EdSheeran-ChrisHemsworth-Getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/EdSheeran-ChrisHemsworth-Getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/EdSheeran-ChrisHemsworth-Getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1392px) 100vw, 1392px" /></p><p>两人表演了《大声思考》</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chris-hemsworth-makes-surprise-appearance-as-drummer-at-ed-sheeran-show-in-romania-3786878">克里斯·海姆斯沃斯 (Chris Hemsworth) 在罗马尼亚艾德·希兰 (Ed Sheeran) 演出中以鼓手身份出人意料地亮相，</a>这一消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="1392" height="884" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/EdSheeran-ChrisHemsworth-Getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="艾德·希兰克里斯·海姆斯沃斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/EdSheeran-ChrisHemsworth-Getty.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/EdSheeran-ChrisHemsworth-Getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/EdSheeran-ChrisHemsworth-Getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/EdSheeran-ChrisHemsworth-Getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/EdSheeran-ChrisHemsworth-Getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1392px) 100vw, 1392px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chris-hemsworth">克里斯·海姆斯沃斯</a>作为客座鼓手意外出现在罗马尼亚<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ed-sheeran">艾德·希兰的</a>音乐会上。请参阅下面晚上的录像。</p><p>昨天（8 月 24 日），希兰在国家体育场向 7 万名观众表演，正如他在<a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/C_EQWvOiVce/?hl=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Instagram</a>上分享的视频中透露的那样，这位<em>《复仇者联盟》</em>演员的亮相从去年 12 月起就已计划好了。</p><p>海姆斯沃斯通过电子邮件请求在他的节目<em>《与克里斯·海姆斯沃斯的无限》</em>中表演鼓，该节目目前正在拍摄第二季。该剧讲述了海姆斯沃斯尝试新体验的故事。</p><p>在第一季中，通过基因测试发现该演员 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/chris-hemsworth-genetic-predisposition-alzheimers-3351798">具有阿尔茨海默病的遗传倾向</a>——这为该剧的前提奠定了基础，旨在提高人们对这种疾病的认识。</p><p>海姆斯沃斯在音乐会之前学会了打鼓。 “我一直在想这个问题，”他在视频中半开玩笑地对希兰说道。随后，两人为布加勒斯特的观众表演了《Thinking Out Loud》。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C_EQWvOiVce/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3